flowRoot.flowPara: Towards an Fire Early Warning System for Indonesia (ToFEWSI)
Land cover and land use information is critical for modelling fire activity in Indonesia
Tadas Nikonovas (1), Allan Spessa (1), and Symon Mezbahuddin (2)
(1) Swansea University, College of Science, Geography Department, Swansea, United Kingdom (tadas.nik@gmail.com),
(2) Department of Renewable Resources, University of Alberta, Canada
This study explores if extreme peatland and forest burning events can be predicted by supervised learning methods using fire weather indices and available land use datasets.
